Developed in Kotlin with Google Firebase Services. It uses Google Realtime DB for data storage regarding teachers and students as well 
as a host of other Firebase services like Firebase Authentication Firebase Cloud Messaging and more. The application is developed in Android
Studio. It supports landscape views and handles the android lifecycle. Some screenshots for some of the pages already developed and 
functioning are 

